text: Birger Stenman (9 October 1909 - 24 April 1989) was a Finnish gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1989 deaths Category:Finnish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Finland Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vyborg
